Name: They Came From the Sky 2
About the game: They Came From the Sky 2 is highly-addictive and fast paced arcade game wherein you take the role of one of the giant Alien robot with one and only one Mission: Features: A excellent Family Alien friendly coffee-break game! Inspired by the legendary game from Amiga: Walker and old good Defender Simple controls and pure arcade action Infinite replayability as you chase ever higher scores! Plenty of delicious humans to abduct Over 20 brutal enemy types like: Grandpa, Skateboard Kid, or disabled person on Wheelchair 50 Human hidden Artifacts waiting to be discovered :O Unlock New Weapons and special abilities in the Tech-Lab Handcrafted pixel graphics created with love Great music by Kevin MacLeod Full Xbox 360 controller support Includes Steam Achievements and of course, Elvises! Warning : This game contains elements of PIXEL violence :O
